IDLULE nemiphefumulo yabantu abathathu ingozi embandakanya iloli neveni emgwaqweni onguthelawayeka, uN2 KwaMbonambi eMpangeni, izolo emini. Abezimo eziphuthumayo, iKwazulu Private Service, babizelwe endaweni yesehlakalo beyotakula abalimele kule ngozi. Umkhulumeli wabo, uMnuz Craig Botha uthe bafike kule ndawo isimo sisibi, iveni itholane phezulu neloli. Iveni ishayise maqede yaphenduka umfunzana. “Abezimo eziphuthumayo bafike endaweni yesehlakalo bagibela phezu komsebenzi wokuhlenga abalimele. Bathole ukuthi umuntu oyedwa okungumshayeli weloli ube nemihuzukwana. Ngeshwa abantu abathathu abebehamba ngeveni bashonile,” kusho uBotha. Uthe abantu abathathu bafe ujuqu bengakafiki nabezimo eziphuthumayo endaweni yesehlakalo. UBotha uthe umshayeli weveni ulashwe esendaweni yesehlakalo, wabe  esedluliselwa esibhedlela. Kuphazamiseke ukuhamba kwezimoto emgwaqweni ngenkathi kwenziwa utakulo. Kwesinye isigameko, kulimale abantu ababili ababehamba ngeloli emgwaqweni uR33 eJabulani eMpangeni ngoMsombuluko. UBotha uthe abezimo eziphuthumayo bafike endaweni yesehlakalo bathola ukuthi iloli iphaphalazile yaphuma emgwaqweni, yagingqika. Uthe kulimale abantu abantu ababili engozi, abalashwe besendaweni yesehlakalo, base sebedluliselwa esibhedlela.